16 THE GIST OF THE PROPOSITION IS AS FOLLOWS:
17 This measure amends Section 3 of Article 7-B of the Oklahoma
18 Constitution. It changes provisions related to the Judicial
19 Nominating Commission. It updates references so that
20 appointments made by certain persons based on the congressional
21 districts would be made using the current congressional
22 districts instead of the districts as the districts were
23 constituted when this section of the Constitution was originally
24 adopted in 1967. It removes a prohibition on certain members of
