1 the Commission so that the person could be a licensed attorney.
2 It allows a person to service on the Commission even if they
3 have a member of their family who is a licensed attorney. It
4 changes the terms so that with one exception the term would be
5 for six (6) years. It removes restrictions based on political
6 party membership. It removes a provision that prohibits a
7 member of the Commission from succeeding himself or herself on
8 the Commission.
